 Navinder Singh Sarao , 37 , is facing extradition and is wanted by American prosecutors after allegedly causing the 2010 Wall Street ` flash crash ' and making more than £ 26 million using a fraudulent trading technique .
He , of Hounslow , west London appeared at Westminster Magistrates ' Court on Wednesday and was bailed with a surety of £ 5 million .
He is accused of using computer programs to create ` spoof ' transactions on the Chicago Mercantile Exchange .